entries.journal_entry_description: Lt. Jasper of CorSec asks that you speak with Major Alana Walden in Tyrena.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Someone is attemping to contact you. Please wait for the signal to be resolved.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Incoming Communication. Please Hold for Signal...
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Greetings. A colleague of mine in Tyrena has some open case files that I thought you might be able to help her with. Head over to Tyrena and speak with Major Alana Walden. Lt. Jasper out.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: A comm. from Lt. Jasper: "Greetings. A colleague of mine in Tyrena has some open case files that I thought you might be able to help her with. Head over to Tyrena and speak with Major Alana Walden. Lt. Jasper out."
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Go speak with Major Alana Walden in Tyrena.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Speak with Major Walden in Tyrena
